==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*μάρτυς / martus / mar'-toos

===Etymology===
*Of uncertain affinity; a witness (literally [judicially] or figuratively [generally]); by analogy a “martyr”: 

===Noun===
'''μάρτυς'''

# [[martyr]], [[record]], [[witness]].

